1d:T6ee,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Can Katie handle emergency electrical calls?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Katie is trained to identify electrical emergencies (no power, burning smell, sparking, shock risk) and marks them as highest priority. You'll get an immediate WhatsApp alert with an emergency tag so you can respond within minutes."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does AI call handling work for EICR and landlord certificates?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Katie recognises landlord and letting agent enquiries by asking the right questions. She captures property portfolio size, certificate type (EICR, PAT, fire alarm), number of properties, and urgency. These are tagged as 'landlord' in your dashboard for fast bulk follow-up."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can customers book appointments directly?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Katie can check your calendar availability and offer specific time slots. When a customer confirms, the appointment is saved to your dashboard and both parties receive confirmation messages."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What if I need to call the customer back first?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Tap 'Call Back' in your WhatsApp alert. Katie sends the customer an SMS with your estimated callback time. When you're ready, the customer's number and full job details are one tap away."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is there a setup fee for electricians?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No setup fee. The £59/month Starter plan includes everything: AI answering, WhatsApp alerts, enquiry dashboard, and review collection. You can be live and taking calls within 30 minutes of signup."}}]}1e:T4f6,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"HowTo","name":"How to Set Up AI Call Handling for Electricians","description":"Four-step process to get Katie answering calls for your electrician business","totalTime":"PT30M","supply":[{"@type":"HowToSupply","name":"UK phone number or existing business line"}],"tool":[{"@type":"HowToTool","name":"Smartphone with WhatsApp"}],"step":[{"@type":"HowToStep","position":1,"name":"Customer calls about an electrical issue","text":"Katie answers with your branded greeting and immediately asks whether it's an emergency (no power, sparking, burning smell) or routine work"},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":2,"name":"Job details captured in 45 seconds","text":"Postcode, property type, job category (fault finding, rewiring, EICR, EV charger, etc.), and whether it's a landlord or homeowner"},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":3,"name":"Smart alert sent to your phone","text":"WhatsApp message with full context: 'Emergency fault — no power — 3-bed house — SE22 — landlord — callback urgently'"},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":4,"name":"Accept and book, or queue for tomorrow","text":"Tap to accept, schedule a callback with time preference, or queue for your next available slot — customer gets confirmation instantly"}]}13:[[["$","script","0",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$1d"}}],["$","script","1",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$1e"}}],["$","script","2",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Service\",\"name\":\"AI Call Handling for Electricians\",\"description\":\"AI call handling for UK electricians. Katie answers 24/7, qualifies jobs, and sends WhatsApp alerts. Never miss a £500+ job again. Free trial.\",\"provider\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Whoza.ai\",\"url\":\"https://whoza.ai\"},\"areaServed\":{\"@type\":\"Country\",\"name\":\"United Kingdom\"},\"hasOfferCatalog\":{\"@type\":\"OfferCatalog\",\"name\":\"Whoza Pricing Plans\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"itemOffered\":{\"@type\":\"Service\",\"name\":\"Starter Plan\"},\"price\":\"59\",\"priceCurrency\":\"GBP\",\"priceValidUnti